WEBVTT

00:00:16.960 --> 00:00:18.879
Maybe I should buy a ticket and go with you.

00:00:20.039 --> 00:00:20.760
No need.

00:00:21.160 --> 00:00:22.199
The two of us can manage.

00:00:23.879 --> 00:00:25.000
Alright, then.

00:00:25.960 --> 00:00:27.039
You two be careful.

00:00:28.920 --> 00:00:30.000
As for the provincial hospital,

00:00:30.079 --> 00:00:31.320
if they find anything,

00:00:31.399 --> 00:00:32.719
I'll tell you right away.

00:00:34.479 --> 00:00:35.200
Paopao.

00:00:35.600 --> 00:00:37.359
Go play over there for a bit, okay?

00:00:37.960 --> 00:00:39.719
Mommy and Daddy need to talk.

00:00:39.920 --> 00:00:41.560
I'm watching you. Don't go too far.

00:00:41.759 --> 00:00:42.439
Go on.

00:00:47.079 --> 00:00:49.719
With exams, treatment, and medication,

00:00:49.799 --> 00:00:51.600
there'll be plenty of costs ahead.

00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:53.439
At work,

00:00:53.840 --> 00:00:54.759
you've got to hold it together.

00:00:56.200 --> 00:00:56.880
Okay.

00:00:57.240 --> 00:00:58.439
Paopao's illness

00:01:02.679 --> 00:01:04.079
is likely a long battle.

00:01:19.319 --> 00:01:20.120
Our girl bought this for you.

00:01:20.200 --> 00:01:21.200
She was too shy to give it to you.

00:01:21.359 --> 00:01:22.159
Take it.

00:01:23.359 --> 00:01:24.200
Come here, Paopao.

00:01:24.640 --> 00:01:26.159
Say goodbye to Daddy.

00:01:28.760 --> 00:01:29.920
Bye, Daddy.

00:01:34.120 --> 00:01:34.719
Come here.

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:35.760
Come on.

00:01:35.799 --> 00:01:36.480
Give me a hug.

00:01:37.760 --> 00:01:38.439
A hug.

00:01:40.120 --> 00:01:41.319
Listen to Mommy, okay?

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:45.799
Text me when you get there.

00:01:49.760 --> 00:01:50.799
Okay, we're heading off.

00:01:51.519 --> 00:01:52.200
Bye-bye.

00:01:53.799 --> 00:01:54.920
Let's go, come on.

00:01:55.120 --> 00:01:56.439
Hold Mommy's hand.

00:02:05.040 --> 00:02:06.480
Watch your step, watch your step.

00:02:09.879 --> 00:02:10.719
Head back inside.

00:02:13.199 --> 00:02:13.879
Let's go.

00:02:26.599 --> 00:02:27.439
Lawyer Luo.

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:28.759
Get in.

00:02:40.879 --> 00:02:41.639
Good timing.

00:02:41.960 --> 00:02:44.000
Just wrapped up. I'll drop you off.

00:03:03.360 --> 00:03:04.159
Lawyer Luo,

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:06.280
how's Bro Mao doing lately?

00:03:08.759 --> 00:03:09.520
He's fine.

00:03:11.080 --> 00:03:12.560
Bro Mao told me to keep an eye on you all.

00:03:12.840 --> 00:03:13.639
He said,

00:03:13.879 --> 00:03:14.919
don't stick your neck out,

00:03:15.439 --> 00:03:16.319
everyone keep a low profile.

00:03:22.039 --> 00:03:24.400
By the way, last time you said...

00:03:24.960 --> 00:03:26.319
why did Bro Mao send you to the cemetery?

00:03:30.159 --> 00:03:31.080
To sweep the tombs.

00:03:34.360 --> 00:03:35.280
You don't believe me?

00:03:39.960 --> 00:03:41.360
Good, you shouldn't.

00:03:41.639 --> 00:03:43.240
Even I don't believe it myself.

00:03:45.840 --> 00:03:47.560
But the jobs Bro Mao gives me

00:03:47.840 --> 00:03:48.800
are pretty terrifying.

00:03:52.479 --> 00:03:54.080
And they look pretty legit.

00:03:56.919 --> 00:03:57.680
Lawyer Luo,

00:03:58.039 --> 00:03:59.400
your place is a left up ahead, right?

00:04:02.960 --> 00:04:04.039
Just pull over here.

00:04:04.120 --> 00:04:05.719
The road ahead is narrow, hard to get through.

00:04:11.719 --> 00:04:12.479
Thanks.

00:04:15.919 --> 00:04:17.399
Let me remind you, Lawyer Luo,

00:04:18.639 --> 00:04:20.199
whether it's Bro Mao or you,

00:04:21.399 --> 00:04:23.360
we're all in the same boat now.

00:04:53.160 --> 00:04:54.000
Young man,

00:04:54.240 --> 00:04:55.639
is it okay to put this here?

00:04:56.600 --> 00:04:57.399
Yeah, that works.

00:04:58.959 --> 00:05:01.160
You're giving me ten percent,

00:05:01.319 --> 00:05:02.680
so how do you make money?

00:05:02.800 --> 00:05:03.600
Well, I

00:05:03.759 --> 00:05:05.120
rely on the advertising.

00:05:05.319 --> 00:05:06.759
How about this, bro, I'll set aside

00:05:07.079 --> 00:05:08.360
ten of them for you, okay?

00:05:08.720 --> 00:05:10.120
Ten percent cash back for you.

00:05:15.279 --> 00:05:16.759
Auto repair, inspections, insurance.

00:05:16.839 --> 00:05:17.639
Check it out.

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:18.519
Bro,

00:05:18.720 --> 00:05:19.439
we've got a new boss.

00:05:19.920 --> 00:05:21.279
There's a promotion going on right now.

00:05:21.319 --> 00:05:22.480
Pay 500, get 2,000.

00:05:22.639 --> 00:05:23.360
Wanna check it out?

00:05:23.480 --> 00:05:24.000
That cheap?

00:05:24.079 --> 00:05:24.800
Cheap, real cheap.

00:05:24.959 --> 00:05:25.800
Come, this way.

00:05:25.959 --> 00:05:26.759
For real?

00:05:26.920 --> 00:05:27.800
Yeah, for real.

00:05:27.920 --> 00:05:28.839
Don't mess with me.

00:05:31.279 --> 00:05:32.879
Alright, since you're so sincere,

00:05:32.959 --> 00:05:34.000
I'll give it a try.

00:05:34.120 --> 00:05:34.920
Thanks so much, see you.

00:05:34.920 --> 00:05:35.519
See you around.

00:05:35.519 --> 00:05:36.759
Great, great, let's make money together.

00:05:36.759 --> 00:05:37.600
Just call this number.

00:05:37.680 --> 00:05:38.079
Alright, got it.

00:05:53.079 --> 00:05:54.160
Here, right here.

00:07:07.560 --> 00:07:08.079
Captain Zhang.

00:07:08.160 --> 00:07:09.639
Chen Yongjiang's phone signal just popped up.

00:07:09.839 --> 00:07:10.439
When?

00:07:10.519 --> 00:07:11.199
Just now.

00:07:11.800 --> 00:07:13.079
You get some rest. Zhao Dian and I will go.

00:07:13.319 --> 00:07:13.879
Okay.

00:07:18.120 --> 00:07:18.839
Sir.

00:07:19.480 --> 00:07:20.800
Do you think Chen Yongjiang

00:07:21.360 --> 00:07:22.680
could be hiding in the residential building?

00:07:25.079 --> 00:07:25.759
Come here.

00:07:27.240 --> 00:07:28.000
Let me ask you,

00:07:29.079 --> 00:07:30.519
even if he's in a residential building,

00:07:31.160 --> 00:07:32.560
we can't tip him off, right?

00:07:32.959 --> 00:07:33.480
Am I right?

00:07:33.480 --> 00:07:35.040
Look, the terrain here is complicated.

00:07:35.759 --> 00:07:36.560
If we rush in,

00:07:36.639 --> 00:07:38.879
he's in the dark and we're exposed.

00:07:39.079 --> 00:07:40.000
Then it'd be even harder to track him.

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:40.839
You get it?

00:07:41.360 --> 00:07:41.879
So...

00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:42.920
So what do we do now?

00:07:43.959 --> 00:07:45.120
Let me see your phone.

00:07:52.000 --> 00:07:52.800
Go on, ask.

00:07:55.040 --> 00:07:55.680
Ask.

00:08:09.199 --> 00:08:09.879
Officer.

00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:11.560
So, what brings you here?

00:08:11.680 --> 00:08:13.519
Nothing much. Just checking the phones you took in recently.

00:08:14.040 --> 00:08:14.879
Phones, huh?

00:08:15.879 --> 00:08:17.160
They're all here. Have a look.

00:08:18.439 --> 00:08:19.560
Investigating a case, Officer?

00:08:20.279 --> 00:08:21.639
Just stopping by, nothing serious.

00:08:22.079 --> 00:08:22.720
Stopping by.

00:08:24.079 --> 00:08:24.920
They're all here.

00:08:25.519 --> 00:08:26.439
All of them.

00:08:26.680 --> 00:08:27.839
For a small shop like ours,

00:08:28.120 --> 00:08:29.560
this counts as good business.

00:08:32.159 --> 00:08:33.440
From what I can see,

00:08:33.559 --> 00:08:34.480
your business can't be bad.

00:08:35.759 --> 00:08:38.480
You've got PC towers and monitors set up.

00:08:39.360 --> 00:08:40.320
And this sofa...

00:08:40.600 --> 00:08:41.519
is about to fall apart.

00:08:41.919 --> 00:08:42.799
Just scraping by.

00:08:43.279 --> 00:08:44.279
Life isn't easy.

00:08:45.120 --> 00:08:47.200
Everything here is legit, right?

00:08:49.879 --> 00:08:50.639
Le-

00:08:51.200 --> 00:08:52.279
Legit, yes.

00:08:52.480 --> 00:08:53.399
All legit.

00:08:54.399 --> 00:08:55.799
Relax, I'm not here for that.

00:08:56.440 --> 00:08:57.200
How about

00:08:57.480 --> 00:08:58.519
you take another look?

00:08:59.279 --> 00:09:00.960
Maybe you forgot something.

00:09:01.240 --> 00:09:02.440
A few more phones somewhere?

00:09:03.200 --> 00:09:04.200
Well, um...

00:09:04.360 --> 00:09:05.519
Let me think.

00:09:06.559 --> 00:09:07.559
Let me check.

00:09:11.759 --> 00:09:12.279
Look,

00:09:12.279 --> 00:09:14.279
a friend left this here a few days ago.

00:09:14.399 --> 00:09:15.639
Look at my memory.

00:09:15.639 --> 00:09:17.159
I just remembered. Look at this.

00:09:17.399 --> 00:09:18.080
A few days ago,

00:09:18.080 --> 00:09:19.919
a friend asked me for a favor.

00:09:21.519 --> 00:09:23.159
You've got a lot of friends.

00:09:27.120 --> 00:09:27.840
Sir.

00:09:28.639 --> 00:09:29.679
Chen Yongjiang's phone.

00:09:32.799 --> 00:09:33.720
Who gave it to you?

00:09:34.360 --> 00:09:35.240
This phone...

00:09:35.720 --> 00:09:36.519
This morning,

00:09:36.639 --> 00:09:38.279
a guy in a hat said

00:09:38.639 --> 00:09:40.120
he fished a phone out of the sea.

00:09:40.120 --> 00:09:41.320
Asked if I could fix it.

00:09:42.519 --> 00:09:44.159
Any surveillance cameras around here?

00:09:45.320 --> 00:09:47.200
No way there's cameras in this area.

00:09:47.440 --> 00:09:48.600
You got his contact info, right?

00:09:49.799 --> 00:09:51.720
Contact info... let me find it.

00:09:52.840 --> 00:09:54.360
I should've written it down.

00:09:55.759 --> 00:09:56.399
Right.

00:09:56.720 --> 00:09:57.440
This is it.

00:10:01.080 --> 00:10:03.120
I was right around here.

00:10:03.399 --> 00:10:05.360
Just drifting around this area.

00:10:05.720 --> 00:10:07.320
Got a bite really quick.

00:10:07.399 --> 00:10:08.720
Barely any time at all.

00:10:08.879 --> 00:10:10.320
Looked like there were tons of fish.

00:10:10.480 --> 00:10:12.279
So I figured I'd cast a net.

00:10:12.759 --> 00:10:14.240
On the second cast,

00:10:14.519 --> 00:10:15.679
up came the phone.

00:10:16.879 --> 00:10:18.720
You sure run into all sorts of things, huh?

00:10:19.519 --> 00:10:21.480
I'm definitely not going back to that reservoir.

00:10:21.600 --> 00:10:22.960
Figured I'd try somewhere else.

00:10:23.360 --> 00:10:25.039
The phone looked pretty decent,

00:10:25.159 --> 00:10:26.200
so I figured I'd find a shop

00:10:26.279 --> 00:10:28.159
to fix it up and see if it still works.

00:10:28.679 --> 00:10:29.240
Officer,

00:10:29.320 --> 00:10:31.000
I didn't cause any trouble, did I?

00:10:31.200 --> 00:10:32.679
No, you actually helped.

00:10:34.080 --> 00:10:34.720
Hold on.

00:10:35.080 --> 00:10:36.600
They just built a new dock nearby,

00:10:37.039 --> 00:10:38.519
so this area's been abandoned.

00:10:38.679 --> 00:10:39.720
Hardly any cameras,

00:10:40.200 --> 00:10:41.039
hardly any people.

00:10:41.919 --> 00:10:43.399
You sure know how to pick your spots.

00:10:43.840 --> 00:10:44.480
Zhao Dian.

00:10:45.200 --> 00:10:45.840
Zhao Dian.

00:10:48.720 --> 00:10:51.159
Isn't that the house where Luo Xiao

00:10:51.279 --> 00:10:52.799
stayed during his vacation?

00:10:54.200 --> 00:10:55.519
Yes, that's the one.

00:10:59.639 --> 00:11:00.720
Check Luo Xiao's movements

00:11:00.720 --> 00:11:02.080
over the past few days, right now.

00:11:19.559 --> 00:11:20.279
Hey, brother-in-law.

00:11:23.279 --> 00:11:24.200
Got a minute?

00:11:26.440 --> 00:11:27.679
Nothing big, just...

00:11:28.639 --> 00:11:30.440
Can you come down to the station in a bit?

00:11:34.600 --> 00:11:35.360
Sure.

00:11:35.519 --> 00:11:37.039
When is a good time for me to go?

00:11:38.279 --> 00:11:39.159
Right now.

00:11:40.559 --> 00:11:41.159
Okay.

00:11:41.519 --> 00:11:42.960
I'll wrap up what I'm doing

00:11:43.039 --> 00:11:43.840
and head over.

00:11:43.919 --> 00:11:44.600
See you soon.

00:11:44.840 --> 00:11:45.440
Alright.